      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Full length outdoor shot in the farmyard of a rural house: four women in rural clothes are holding pieces of clothes in their hands; one of them is also holding a round sieve. On the left next to them a man is playing the violin. On the right a man in rural clothes with a pistol attached to his belt is standing. Behind this group of people a woman and a man are standing. On the wooden stairs there are two women standing, one of them is holding an infant in her arms. A girl, resting her arms on a wooden parapet with clothes on and over it is looking down from the terrace on the second floor of the house.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Gift to the National Ethnographic Museum from the Bulgarian Ethnographic Society (Balgarsko narodouchno druzhestvo).</ab>
